sentences.english: A family in Grain Valley, Missouri, is trying to adopt him, "We can love him."

sentences.english: The previous record was a 130-pound catfish caught in Missouri last year.
sentences.chinese: 之前的記錄是去年密蘇里州捕獲的重130磅的鮎魚。

sentences.english: This shot was taken at the City Museum in St.

sentences.english: Later Monday he is heading to  Missouri.

sentences.english: And the state of Missouri has adopted its own veterinary -student loan programme.
sentences.chinese: 密蘇里州已經通過了關於該州獸醫學學生貸款的計劃。

sentences.english: Scott lived in these two places for almost four years before he was returned to Missouri.
sentences.chinese: 斯科特在回到密蘇里州之前在這兩個地方居住了四年。

sentences.english: The shortest distance between Missouri and California was across the central part of the country.

sentences.english: The research is sponsored by St. Louis University in Missouri and by Wichita State.

sentences.english: Zane will attend Saint Louis University in Missouri and major in biology this fall.

sentences.english: In his twenties he settled in Sedalia, Missouri.
sentences.chinese: 多歲時他在密蘇里州的錫代利亞地區定居。

sentences.english: What type are you? Corn-fed , salt-of-the-earth Missouri guy.

sentences.english: There was a big company located in St. Louis, Missouri.

sentences.english: A city of western Missouri, a suburb of Kansas City.
